    "\n",
    "### Business Understanding\n",
    "\n",
    "### Determine Business Objectives\n",
    "#### Background\n",
    "   \n",
    "This application explores a dataset from Kaggle, containing information on 426K used cars.\n",
    "The goal is to understand what factors make a car more or less expensive and as a result of the analysis, provide clear \n",
    "recommendations to the client -- a used car dealership -- as to what consumers value in a used car.[Summarized from the assignment](https://classroom.emeritus.org/courses/13195/assignments/417295?module_item_id=3147260)\n",
    "    \n",
    "#### Business Objectives\n",
    "     \n",
    "Given the profile picture, this is a used car lot. The goal is to study what features drive the cost of a car, and use that data to increase sale profits.  \n",
    "\n",
    "#### Business Success Criteria\n",
    "     \n",
    "This data set has no information about sales - dates, time of sale, weather, etc. Therefore this study is a preliminary analsis from which the dealeaship can implement targeted strategies based on the most valuable car features to see if the sales increase. This is an iterative process, so once applied we will have sales data form which to fine tune the parameters of the sales strategy.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Assess Situation\n",
    "#### Invetory of Resources\n",
    "All data is from the vehicles.csv file.\n",
    "####  Requirements, Assumtptions and Contraints\n",
    "For this study we are assuming that the data is accurate, and in particular the price of the vehicles are true and not speculative.\n",
    "            \n",
    "#### Risks and Contengentcies\n",
    "\n",
    " Risk | Contengency| \n",
    "| -------- | -------- \n",
    "| The project is dependent on having time during the work week to do all the background work.| I am prepared to take Thursday off from work to meet the deadline | \n",
    "| The most recent car is 2022. A quick google search revealed that car prices have increased 3.5% by early 2026 | It might be good to increase the prices by 3.5%  | \n",
    "| Data Science services have a cost. The cost of analysis must be recooped by increased sales.| This is an iterative process, the dealer may terminate services at any time. |\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Terminology\n",
    "##### [Business Terminology](https://www.workspace.co.uk/content-hub/business-insight/glossary-of-business-terminology)    (Workspace&copy;)\n",
    "##### [Data Mining Terminology](https://twocrows.com/data-mining/dm-glossary/) (Two Crows Consulting&copy;)\n",
    "#### Cost and Benetits\n",
    "If the cost of the analysis is N, then there must be a N * 1.20 benefit. This is the point where the cost of collecting the data, and training the sales team to implement the data based strategies will be worth the effort.\n",
    "### Determing Data Mining Goals\n",
    "####  Data Mining Goals\n",
    "Produce a manageable set of five or less features that are correlated with increased price of cars. \n",
    "####  Data Mining Success Criteria\n",
    "Producing a set of actionable features which the sales force feel confident working with.\n",
    "### Produce Project Plan\n",
    "Analyze the data to summarize it. \n",
    "Use analysis techniques to determine best parameters .\n",
    "####  Project Plan\n",
    "Describe what you will do in the pyton analysis code\n",
    "Through multi factor regression determine as best as possible which factors and combination of factors show positive correlations with higher sales.\n",
    "#### Initial Assessment of Tools and Techniques\n",
    "   \n",
    "Through multi factor regression determine as best as possible which factors and combination of factors show positive correlations with higher sales.  "
   ]
