    "### Plan Deployment\n",
    "#### Deployment Plan\n",
    "Preliminary analysis showed that the year of the car is positively associated with price, and the type of truck, paired with fuel efficienty are good predictors of price. It is our recomendation for the first iteration of our study to emphasize trucks with relatively high miles per gallon. \n",
    "### Plan Monitoring and Maintenance\n",
    "The predicitve power of our model was not what we hope for, so there needs to be more focused analysis in the future.  Cars rangs from 1905 to 2022, have range in price from 500 to a 155,000 mercedes benz. These outliers are making a model difficult, and we suggest focusing on cars in a more focused price range (15000m to 60,000) and year (1990 to 2022)\n",
    "#### Monitoring and Maintenance Plan\n",
    "We will be monitoring the sales figures to see if we move more trucks in the coming month, then we will return with more focued analysis and suggestions. \n",
